Join-condition: A.XACTION_SOURCE_MASTER_ID=B.NO AND (B.INV_DATE=A.XACTION_DATE OR B.INV_DATE=A.XACTION_DUE_DATE) AND A.XACTION_SOURCE_MASTER_TYPE in ('ACOREUS INV NO', 'INVOICE NO', 'PRE DUNNING REF NO')
Name: A10

Join-condition: A.XACTION_SOURCE_VOUCHER_ID=B.NO AND (B.INV_DATE=A.XACTION_DATE OR B.INV_DATE=A.XACTION_DUE_DATE) AND A.XACTION_SOURCE_VOUCHER_TYPE in ('ACOREUS INV NO', 'INVOICE NO', 'PRE DUNNING REF NO')
Name: A11

Join-condition: (CASE WHEN A.XACTION_SOURCE_VOUCHER_TYPE = 'INVOICE DATA OID' THEN BIGINT(A.XACTION_SOURCE_VOUCHER_ID) ELSE null END)=B.OID AND A.XACTION_SOURCE_VOUCHER_ID=RTRIM(CHAR(B.OID))
Name: A13

Join-condition: (CASE WHEN A.XACTION_SOURCE_MEDIA_TYPE = 'INVOICE DATA OID' THEN BIGINT(A.XACTION_SOURCE_MEDIA_ID) ELSE null END)=B.OID AND A.XACTION_SOURCE_VOUCHER_ID=RTRIM(CHAR(B.OID))
Name: A14

Join-condition: (CASE WHEN A.XACTION_SOURCE_MEDIA_TYPE = 'BELEGNUMMER_TEILFORDERUNG' THEN INT(A.XACTION_SOURCE_MASTER_ID) ELSE null END)=B.MOVEMENT_ID AND A.XACTION_SOURCE_MASTER_ID=RTRIM(CHAR(B.MOVEMENT_ID))
Name: A15

Join-condition: (CASE WHEN A.XACTION_SOURCE_VOUCHER_TYPE = 'PRE DUNNING REF NO' THEN INT(SUBSTR(A.XACTION_SOURCE_VOUCHER_ID, 5)) ELSE null END)=B.REFERENCE_ID AND SUBSTR(A.XACTION_SOURCE_VOUCHER_ID, 1, 3)=B.PREFIX AND B.PREFIX || ' ' || RTRIM(CHAR(B.REFERENCE_ID))=A.XACTION_SOURCE_VOUCHER_ID
Name: A16

Join-condition: (CASE WHEN A.XACTION_SOURCE_VOUCHER_TYPE in ('BT-LOC-INV-POS','BT-ACO-DEB-ORD','BT-ACO-BNK-CRD','BT-ACO-INV-POS','BT-ACO-OCH-CNS','BT-VNB-DUN-POS') THEN INT(A.XACTION_SOURCE_VOUCHER_ID) ELSE null END)=B.VOUCHER_ID AND A.XACTION_SOURCE_VOUCHER_ID=RTRIM(CHAR(B.VOUCHER_ID))
Name: A19

Join-condition: (CASE WHEN A.XACTION_SOURCE_MEDIA_TYPE in ('BT-ACO-CRD-POS','ACCOUNT POSTING','BT-ACO-PAY-CNS') THEN INT(A.XACTION_SOURCE_MEDIA_ID) ELSE null END)=B.VOUCHER_ID AND A.XACTION_SOURCE_MEDIA_ID=RTRIM(CHAR(B.VOUCHER_ID))
Name: A20
